Charlotte Beaumont https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charlotte_Beaumont 0 Charlotte Beaumont (born 28 July 1995) is an English actress known for portraying Chloe Latimer on the ITV crime drama Broadchurch, as well as roles in Waterloo Road, and the film Jupiter Ascending.
